metadata.name: tree_135
metadata.description:
A collection of unique retro-futuristic holographic trees designed to represent an individual's personal family tree data (including memories, consciousness, and genetic information), when it is uploaded to the cloud in a future time. 

This is the digital icon for your family's tree of life.

An A.I was trained to spawn trees based on a small set of digital illustrations by Sutu. Each artwork was then manually processed and edited with additional illustration for aesthetic consistency.
